All 9 bugs fixed. TypeScript check and build both pass cleanly. Here's a summary:

### Bug 1/4 (Critical): Chat History & Cross-Location Data Leak
**`src/lib/vectorStore.ts`** — The code called `supabase.rpc('match_documents', { p_tenant_id, p_store_id })` but the SQL function is `match_document_chunks` with parameters `match_tenant_id` and `match_store_id`. This caused:
- Vector search to fail entirely (wrong function name)
- Store-scoped filtering to not apply (wrong parameter names defaulting to NULL)
- Fixed both the function name and all parameter names

### Bug 2: Lease Summary Disappearing
**`src/app/api/lease-summary/route.ts`** — Added error logging instead of silently returning `{ summary: null }` on any error

### Bug 3: Obligation Matrix "Upload Documents First"
**`src/lib/obligationMatrix.ts`** — Removed the regex filter that required obligation-specific language in the fallback path. Now sends ALL chunks (up to 35) when keyword search fails, with better logging for debugging

### Bug 5: Citation Excerpts Mid-Word
**`src/lib/vectorStore.ts`** — Rewrote `cleanExcerpt()` with better word boundary detection:
- Start: detects mid-word starts (lowercase first char) and skips to next word boundary with `…` prefix
- End: trims to last punctuation/space boundary instead of just last space

### Bug 6: Streaming Glitchiness
- **`src/app/globals.css`** — Changed `overflow: hidden` to `overflow-wrap: break-word`, reduced animation from 0.2s→0.15s, raised start opacity from 0.4→0.6
- **`src/app/chat/page.tsx`** — Replaced `requestAnimationFrame` scroll with debounced 80ms `setTimeout` to reduce scroll jank during streaming

### Bug 7: Dashboard Filters
**`src/components/DashboardGrid.tsx`** — State filter now uses `\b` word boundary regex to prevent "CA" matching "CALIFORNIA". Status filter now handles `null` and `NaN` dates gracefully

### Bug 8: Document Preview
- Created **`src/components/DocumentListItem.tsx`** — client component with click-to-preview via signed URLs
- **`src/app/location/[id]/page.tsx`** — Replaced static document divs with `<DocumentListItem>`, removed unused `DOC_TYPE_LABELS`

### Bug 9: Asset Class Auto-Detection
**`src/lib/leaseSummary.ts`** — Added normalization of Claude's asset_class response against valid values, plus error logging if the store update fails
